786
00:48:59,523 --> 00:49:02,644
We had a lot of stuff to do, and yeah,

787
00:49:02,644 --> 00:49:06,125
I don't think I have a good answer for you.

788
00:49:06,125 --> 00:49:08,485
It's something we should probably look at, though,

789
00:49:08,485 --> 00:49:09,825
if there are any other sequels.

790
00:49:09,825 --> 00:49:10,565
Absolutely, yeah.

791
00:49:10,565 --> 00:49:10,966
Next question?

792
00:49:13,267 --> 00:49:21,852
Hi, so Human Revolution is sort of unique in that it was sort of accepted by, mostly

