00:50:05,216 --> 00:50:06,577
It's not how we designed the game.

810
00:50:06,577 --> 00:50:07,697
It's not how it was written.

811
00:50:07,697 --> 00:50:11,620
So if that's the case, it's a coincidence.

812
00:50:11,620 --> 00:50:14,722
As for the fan base and the reason why we got accepted by them...

813
00:50:14,982 --> 00:50:16,543
It's because we did listen to them.

814
00:50:16,543 --> 00:50:22,427
When we went on forums, they were the guys that we were listening to.

815
00:50:22,427 --> 00:50:26,810
We also got people from the community come to see us before the game was finished,

816
00:50:26,810 --> 00:50:28,471
just to see what they thought.

